						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/cme/" rel="tag">CME</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/fine/" rel="tag">fine</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/gasoline/" rel="tag">gasoline</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/jpmorgan/" rel="tag">JPMorgan</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/oil/" rel="tag">Oil</a></span>					</p>
				</div>

