						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/cia/" rel="tag">CIA</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/hormuz/" rel="tag">Hormuz</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/hormuz-strait/" rel="tag">Hormuz Strait</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/iran/" rel="tag">Iran</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/mossad/" rel="tag">Mossad</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/nuclear/" rel="tag">nuclear</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/obama/" rel="tag">Obama</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/oil/" rel="tag">Oil</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/us-navy/" rel="tag">US Navy</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/war/" rel="tag">War</a></span>					</p>
